{
  "stem": "16930.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So-- but this lady took it upon herself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "She wanted to really make my sister into her image, like it would be her daughter.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And she really tried to press upon her more the Christian path and everything else.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And-- and they weren't that anxious.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They were not against my coming at that time, but they weren't doing the-- too many encouragements either.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But I guess they had to because of pressure from my people, whom I was with and from neighbors.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They had to allow some sort of contact.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was only eight years old, barely-- not quite nine when she got there in '39, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she was just not quite nine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was a very shy kid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was a more boisterous, outgoing boy, so we're quite different personalities.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so she was shy and reticent.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think she-- must have been quite a big, traumatic shock to her to be away from my parents and-- and to be there with strangers.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she didn't know any English.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And these people were very-- they wanted to own her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were sweet to her, and kind of coochie-coochie-coo and all that, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and they sort of like treating her like a baby.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I guess they wanted a baby, which never had.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they really weren't interested in her growth and development as much as their getting the satisfaction of having a baby in the house when she was eight going on nine.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and I don't think it was a very happy experience.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Being there was not a happy experience for my sister.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But what could she do, you know, other than make the best of it?",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
